OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777551071
OL,3,CTrial date set for pensioner, 92,
OL,4,Caccused of murdering wife
OL,6,FA trial date has been set for a 92-
OL,7,Fyear-old man accused of murdering his
OL,8,Felderly wife in Devon.
OL,10,FLaurence Billam, of Edwards Court in
OL,11,FMillbrook Lane, Exeter, is charged
OL,12,Fwith killing 87-year-old Shirley
OL,13,FBillam.
OL,15,FHis case was heard before Judge Robert
OL,16,FLinford at Exeter Crown Court on
OL,17,FWednesday morning.
OL,19,FJudge Linford, appearing by video link
OL,20,Ffrom Plymouth Crown Court, set a trial
OL,21,Fdate for October 12.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
