FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777551071
OL,3,CTrial date set for pensioner, 92,
OL,4,Caccused of murdering wife
OL,6,FThe judge said: "The court's
OL,7,Fcondolences go out to the family and
OL,8,Ffriends, and all of those who are
OL,9,Faffected by this tragedy.
OL,11,F"I will identify a plea and trial
OL,12,Fpreparation hearing on May 28 and a
OL,13,Fprovisional trial date on October 12."
OL,15,FNo application for bail was made
OL,16,Fduring the short hearing, which Billam
OL,17,Fdid not attend.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOUuD@fO]
