OL,3,CTrial date set for pensioner, 92,
OL,4,Caccused of murdering wife
OL,6,FHe appeared by video link during a
OL,7,Fhearing at Exeter Magistrates' Court
OL,8,Fon Tuesday, when he spoke only to
OL,9,Fconfirm his name and date of birth.
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall Police previously
OL,12,Fconfirmed that emergency services were
OL,13,Fcalled to an address on Millbrook Lane
OL,14,Fat about 12.40pm on April 19.
OL,16,FThe body of Mrs Billam was discovered
OL,17,Fat the scene.
OL,19,FA force spokesman confirmed Mrs
OL,20,FBillam's family are being supported by
OL,21,Fspecialist officers.
